dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile contains the sub-county (LEVEL5) boundaries for Uganda. The counties of Uganda are divided into sub-counties. This layer is based on 2006 data provided by Ugandan Bureau of Statistics (UBOS) and has been updated recently as Government of Uganda changed Administrative Boundaries to create some new districts in 2010.
